Template-Magic-Pager README File
================================


Description
-----------

Template::Magic::Pager is a HTML pager for Template::Magic. It allows you to split an array into several pages, automating all the process and supplying all the labels to produce linked result pages (Gooooogle style).


Installation
------------

0.  Prerequisites:
- Perl version    >= 5.6.1
- Template::Magic >= 1.2
- OOTools         >= 1.71


1. Standard installation
- from the directory where this file is located, type:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install


